Name: Average time from the start of the process to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'START_EVENT' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Maximum time to complete Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE while it is the first activity
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION when it occurs right after the Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total waiting time for Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in variants where it is not the first activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE when it occurs right before the Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE when the case ends with Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER when the Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER is the last activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to the end of process for the cases where the trip takes place
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'END_EVENT'

Name: Avg time until Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for domestic trips
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE while the request is sent for approval to the travel administration
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for cases with reimbursement of the costs afterwards
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total processing time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Maximum processing time among all activities that can occur after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total process time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'
